-- Green Mountain Coffee Roasters to Restate Financial Statements for Errors
-- B y   S t e f a n i e   B a t c h o - L i n o
-- 2010-11-19T21:22:03Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-11-19/green-mountain-coffee-roasters-to-restate-financial-statements-for-errors.html
Green Mountain Coffee Roasters Inc.
said it will restate previously issued financial statements for
fiscal years 2007, 2008 and 2009 and the first three quarters of
2010 due to errors identified in these financial statements.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Stefanie Batcho-Lino at 
 sbatcholino1@bloomberg.net  